Configurations:
==============
1. New folder Storage in ~ containing following sub folders(this folder will be backed up)
  - Audio
  - Bin
  - Desktop
  - Development
  - Docs
  - Docs/Dropbox
  - Docs/eMail
  - Dotfiles
  - Downloads
  - Pictures
  - Videos
Symlink from ~ to each sub folder of Storage. Backup /Storage folder to /Data/Backups/N73SV - Ubuntu
2. New folder in ~ called Dotfiles (symlink to Storage/Dotfiles)
3. Symlink for .bash_profile to /Dotfiles/bash/.bash_profile
4. Symlink for .gitconfig to /Dotfiles/git/gitconfig/Linux/.gitconfig
5. Symlink for .inputrc to /Dotfiles/bash/.inputrc
6. Symlink for .vimrc to /Dotfiles/vim/.vimrc
7. Configure Dropbox to save data to /Storage/Docs/Dropbox
8. Configure Thunderbird to save emails to /Storage/Docs/eMail (http://kb.mozillazine.org/Moving_your_mail_storage_location_(Thunderbird))
